Check out is 12pm but as our flight wasn't until 10pm they told us that we could leave the bags, use the pool and have a shower in the gym.	The 'gym' consisted of three machines (a stepper, a running machine and a bike) that looked like they were made in the 80s, and any time we tried to access the pool area on the roof the door was locked!!	Great for all the family, swimming pool and lounge on the roof with stunning veiws, also a gym and sauna downstairs.